	"system": {
		"description": "<p>Comfrey features long, simple leaves with fine hairs pointing downward. It has hollow stalks that grow up to five feet high with more coarse hair and bell-shaped violet or white flowers. It grows near water sources, in damp fields and ditches, blooming in late spring. Its roots have a black bark, and when crushed, are very effective for open wounds and restoring strength.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Effect.</strong></em> When applied to a creature suffering from the [[/condition id=incapacitated]] condition, the crushed root immediately enables them to immediately repeat the saving throw against the condition. Note that comfrey does not provide this benefit against the [[/condition id=stunned]] condition.</p>",
